{"word":"Zalmon","slug":"zalmon","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Zalmon</b> <a href=\"#/H6756\">H6756</a> <br/> 1. A hill in Samaria, probably also called Salmon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=9&verse=48'>Jdg 9:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=68&verse=14'>Psa 68:14</a><br/> 2. One of David's warriors<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=28'>2Sa 23:28</a>"}]}